tugaskulah untuk mengarahkannya
ke jalan yang benar.

525
00:33:48,846 --> 00:33:51,014
Tolong jaga dia baik-baik.

526
00:33:51,638 --> 00:33:52,472
Tentu.

527
00:33:55,767 --> 00:33:58,020
JQ SONGJU

528
00:33:58,270 --> 00:33:59,730
Dia dalam perjalanan bisnis.

529
00:34:00,272 --> 00:34:01,398
Perjalanan bisnis?

530
00:34:02,107 --> 00:34:03,108
Ke mana?

531
00:34:03,734 --> 00:34:05,193
Dia di Jerman.

532
00:34:06,445 --> 00:34:09,656
Dia tetap harus datang.
Ayah mertuanya meninggal.

533
00:34:10,449 --> 00:34:11,700
Pasti ada urusan penting.

534
00:34:11,783 --> 00:34:15,621
Kudengar, dia menghadiri forum
soal bisnis energi yang bisa dibarui.

535
00:34:15,704 --> 00:34:17,539
Jam berapa penerbangannya?

536
00:34:18,123 --> 00:34:19,499
