sedang pergi berbisnis?

544
00:34:48,153 --> 00:34:49,363
Ini aku.

545
00:34:49,446 --> 00:34:51,907
Cek catatan keluar dan masuk
bandara Jeong Sang-hun.

546
00:34:52,991 --> 00:34:54,534
Ya. Segera.

547
00:34:57,120 --> 00:34:58,580
Yeong-min.

548
00:34:59,164 --> 00:35:01,249
Kau yakin Sang-hun pergi berbisnis?

549
00:35:01,333 --> 00:35:02,918
Kenapa dia belum meneleponku?

550
00:35:03,085 --> 00:35:04,878
Dia pasti sudah dengar kabar.

551
00:35:04,962 --> 00:35:06,672
<i>Seluruh negara gempar.</i>

552
00:35:06,755 --> 00:35:08,590
<i>Kau percaya Sang-hun belum dengar?</i>

553
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:10,342
Tenanglah dahulu.

554
00:35:10,842 --> 00:35:12,344
Dia pasti punya alasan kuat.

555
00:35:13,553 --> 00:35:14,554
Aku penyebabnya?

556
00:35:15,430 --> 00:35:17,641
Jika dia berusaha menghindariku,

557
00:35:17,724 --> 00:35:19,559
