558
00:35:19,810 --> 00:35:21,812
Kuharap itu masalahnya, Yeong-min.

559
00:35:22,562 --> 00:35:24,773
Seo-hui, kurasa tidak.

560
00:35:25,774 --> 00:35:26,775
Yeong-min.

561
00:35:28,402 --> 00:35:30,946
Kudengar, kamera dasbor mobil Ayah
tidak ada.

562
00:35:31,238 --> 00:35:32,364
