<i>- Hari itu,</i>

563
00:35:32,447 --> 00:35:34,533
Ayah bilang akan menemui Sang-hun.

564
00:35:35,200 --> 00:35:38,912
Lalu beberapa hari lalu,
kulihat mereka bertengkar hebat.

565
00:35:39,329 --> 00:35:40,831
<i>Menakutkan sekali.</i>

566
00:35:41,581 --> 00:35:42,874
Kurasa terjadi sesuatu.

567
00:35:42,958 --> 00:35:44,251
<i>Tunggu.</i>

568
00:35:44,918 --> 00:35:45,836
Apa maksudmu?

569
00:35:47,462 --> 00:35:49,381
Siapa yang kau curigai?

570
00:35:51,842 --> 00:35:52,884
Kau tak apa, Seo-hui?

571
00:35:53,677 --> 00:35:55,262
Yeong-min, aku merasa hampir gila.

572
00:35:56,847 --> 00:35:59,099
Tolong beri tahu aku
setelah Sang-hun meneleponmu.

573
00:35:59,182 --> 00:36:01,059
<i>Kumohon.</i>

574
00:36:02,144 --> 00:36:03,228
Baik.

575
00:36:19,453 --> 00:36:20,620
Hei.

576
00:36:21,580 --> 00:36:22,622
Kaukah?

